Author: j4jackj
Text: I had a situation once where I fainted one and a half times and I puked all over the bath involuntarily afterwards, once. I have no idea why it happened, didn't feel ill after puking at all that time, once I had been on the toilet a bit to recover my homeostasis (had to go anyway so I thought then and there would be an excellent time and place to rest & recover). But yeah. Puking fucking sucks.
